SparQL query for Riksdag members' places of birth

Example for a student

Mar 6, 2025 • 679 min read

dt2112   sparql   riksdag 

FIRST = """
SELECT ?person ?riksdagid ?pob ?pobCoordinates ?swedishWikipedia WHERE {
    ?person wdt:P1214 ?riksdagid.
    OPTIONAL {
        ?person wdt:P19 ?pob.
        OPTIONAL { ?pob wdt:P625 ?pobCoordinates. }
    }
    OPTIONAL {
        ?swedishWikipedia schema:about ?person;
                          schema:isPartOf <https://sv.wikipedia.org/>.
    }
}
"""

QUERY = """
SELECT ?person ?riksdagid ?pob ?pobCoordinates ?swedishWikipedia ?constituency WHERE {
    ?person wdt:P1214 ?riksdagid.

    OPTIONAL {
        ?person wdt:P19 ?pob.
        OPTIONAL { ?pob wdt:P625 ?pobCoordinates. }
    }

    OPTIONAL {
        ?swedishWikipedia schema:about ?person;
                          schema:isPartOf <https://sv.wikipedia.org/>.
    }

    OPTIONAL {
        ?person p:P39 ?positionStatement.
        ?positionStatement ps:P39 wd:Q10655178.
        OPTIONAL { ?positionStatement pq:P768 ?constituency. }
    }
}
"""

import requests

# Define the SPARQL endpoint
WIKIDATA_SPARQL_URL = "https://query.wikidata.org/sparql"

# Define headers to identify the request as a bot
HEADERS = {
    "User-Agent": "WikidataQueryBot/1.0 (your_email@example.com)"
}

# Send the request
response = requests.get(WIKIDATA_SPARQL_URL, params={"query": QUERY, "format": "json"}, headers=HEADERS)

# Check if the request was successful
if response.status_code == 200:
    data = response.json()

    # Print the results
    for item in data["results"]["bindings"]:
        person = item.get("person", {}).get("value", "N/A")
        riksdagid = item.get("riksdagid", {}).get("value", "N/A")
        pob = item.get("pob", {}).get("value", "N/A")
        pob_coordinates = item.get("pobCoordinates", {}).get("value", "N/A")
        swedish_wikipedia = item.get("swedishWikipedia", {}).get("value", "N/A")
        constituency = item.get("constituency", {}).get("value", "N/A")

        print(f"Person: {person}")
        print(f"Riksdag ID: {riksdagid}")
        print(f"Place of Birth: {pob}")
        print(f"Coordinates: {pob_coordinates}")
        print(f"Swedish Wikipedia: {swedish_wikipedia}")
        print(f"Constituency: {constituency}")
        print("-" * 80)
else:
    print(f"Error: {response.status_code}")
